FIELD~SKU~2~Stock Keeping Unit~Unique
FIELD~UPC~3~UPC Barcode~Universal Product Code
FIELD~ITEM.DESC~4~Item Description~
FIELD~ITEM.DESC.LONG~5~Long Description~
FIELD~CATEGORY~6~Product Category~
FIELD~SUBCATEGORY~7~Product Subcategory~
FIELD~BRAND~8~Brand Name~
FIELD~MANUFACTURER~9~Manufacturer~
FIELD~MANUFACTURER.PART~10~Manufacturer Part Number~
FIELD~UNIT.OF.MEASURE~11~Unit of Measure~EA, CS, DZ, LB, etc
FIELD~PACK.SIZE~12~Pack Size~Units per case
FIELD~COST~13~Standard Cost~
FIELD~LAST.COST~14~Last Purchase Cost~
FIELD~AVG.COST~15~Average Cost~
FIELD~PRICE.LEVEL1~16~Retail Price Level 1~
FIELD~PRICE.LEVEL2~17~Retail Price Level 2~
FIELD~PRICE.LEVEL3~18~Retail Price Level 3~
FIELD~PRICE.LEVEL4~19~Wholesale Price Level 4~
FIELD~PRICE.LEVEL5~20~Wholesale Price Level 5~
FIELD~MSRP~21~Manufacturer Suggested Retail Price~
FIELD~MIN.PRICE~22~Minimum Allowed Price~
FIELD~QTY.ON.HAND~23~Quantity On Hand~Multivalued by store
FIELD~QTY.ALLOCATED~24~Quantity Allocated~Multivalued by store
FIELD~QTY.AVAILABLE~25~Quantity Available~Calculated
FIELD~QTY.ON.ORDER~26~Quantity On Purchase Order~
FIELD~REORDER.POINT~27~Reorder Point~Multivalued by store
FIELD~REORDER.QTY~28~Reorder Quantity~
