FIELD~MIN.STOCK.LEVEL~30~Minimum Stock Level~
FIELD~LEAD.TIME~31~Lead Time Days~
FIELD~PREFERRED.VENDOR~32~Preferred Vendor ID~
FIELD~VENDOR.ITEM~33~Vendor Item Number~
FIELD~TAXABLE~34~Taxable Flag~Y/N
FIELD~TAX.CODE~35~Tax Code~
FIELD~SERIALIZED~36~Serialized Item Flag~Y/N
FIELD~LOT.CONTROLLED~37~Lot Controlled Flag~Y/N
FIELD~PERISHABLE~38~Perishable Item Flag~Y/N
FIELD~SHELF.LIFE.DAYS~39~Shelf Life in Days~
FIELD~WEIGHT~40~Weight~
FIELD~WEIGHT.UOM~41~Weight Unit of Measure~LB, KG
FIELD~LENGTH~42~Length~
FIELD~WIDTH~43~Width~
FIELD~HEIGHT~44~Height~
FIELD~DIMENSION.UOM~45~Dimension Unit of Measure~IN, CM
FIELD~CUBE~46~Cubic Feet/Meters~
FIELD~LOCATION~47~Primary Warehouse Location~Multivalued by store
FIELD~BIN.LOCATION~48~Bin Location~Multivalued by store
FIELD~STATUS~49~Item Status~A=Active, I=Inactive, D=Discontinued
FIELD~SALE.START.DATE~50~Sale Start Date~
FIELD~SALE.END.DATE~51~Sale End Date~
FIELD~SALE.PRICE~52~Sale Price~
FIELD~PROMO.CODE~53~Current Promotion Code~
FIELD~COMMISSION.PCT~54~Commission Percentage~
