* Index Definitions
INDEX~SKU.IDX~SKU~SKU Index
INDEX~UPC.IDX~UPC~UPC Barcode Index
INDEX~CATEGORY.IDX~CATEGORY~Category Index
INDEX~BRAND.IDX~BRAND~Brand Index
INDEX~VENDOR.IDX~PREFERRED.VENDOR~Vendor Index
INDEX~STATUS.IDX~STATUS~Status Index
INDEX~DESC.IDX~ITEM.DESC~Description Index

* Correlatives and Derived Fields
CORR~QTY.AVAILABLE.CALC~QTY.ON.HAND - QTY.ALLOCATED
CORR~TOTAL.QTY.ON.HAND~SUM(QTY.ON.HAND)
CORR~TOTAL.QTY.ALLOCATED~SUM(QTY.ALLOCATED)
CORR~TOTAL.QTY.AVAILABLE~TOTAL.QTY.ON.HAND - TOTAL.QTY.ALLOCATED
CORR~INVENTORY.VALUE~TOTAL.QTY.ON.HAND * AVG.COST
CORR~MARKUP.PCT~((PRICE.LEVEL1 - COST) / COST) * 100
CORR~MARGIN.PCT~((PRICE.LEVEL1 - COST) / PRICE.LEVEL1) * 100
CORR~NEEDS.REORDER~IF TOTAL.QTY.AVAILABLE <= REORDER.POINT THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N'
CORR~DAYS.SINCE.SALE~DATE() - LAST.SALE.DATE
CORR~DAYS.SINCE.RECEIPT~DATE() - LAST.RECEIPT.DATE
CORR~ON.SALE~IF DATE() >= SALE.START.DATE AND DATE() <= SALE.END.DATE THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N'
CORR~CURRENT.PRICE~IF ON.SALE THEN SALE.PRICE ELSE PRICE.LEVEL1
